query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('calculus-and-analysis',
'differential-equations',
'inorganic-chemistry',
'physical-chemistry')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('chemistry',
'mathematica')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Caucus',
'Citizen Patrol',
'Critic',
'Curious',
'Custodian',
'Enlightened',
'Famous Question',
'Good Question',
'Necromancer',
'Revival',
'Tumbleweed')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
